{"tid":1679191,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「中美新戰線？」習近平提加快區塊鏈 比特幣急升逾兩成","createTime":"2019-10-28T05:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T05:50:57.000Z","uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c72863084cd1ca8ace300ef422135c21cc7e23f1","tid":1679191,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:09:13.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】虛擬貨幣價格，向來易受政府政策和取態影響。國家主席習近平在上周四會議上表示，將加大力度，加快推動區塊鏈技術和產業創新發展，消息刺激比特幣昨日爆升。據報價平台Coindesk報價，比特幣價格由周五晚上的7600美元水平，至周六日間曾升穿1萬美元，創個半月以來高位，截至昨晚8時半，報9172美元，上升20.34%。有業內人士表示，投資者藉消息扭轉近期弱勢，或有望升穿6月1.2萬美元高位。"},{"pid":"3993e0077e6937152a67eb9897ff976ff8e56af2","tid":1679191,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:09:37.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"803ef9337e1040d6b2d40b731cd697190a934275","tid":1679191,"uid":41873,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5毛又開post啦</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f2f8e7a2587a0f569597da1955a386342d65aa67","tid":1679191,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:11:30.000Z","msg":"朱克伯格搞Libra比美國聽證會係咁質<br />\n有無人估到背後原因係咩"},{"pid":"181ec1e13244d803181b554ea09944af3ad21abb","tid":1679191,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:19:29.000Z","msg":"五毛post <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />